1.Why Subquery:-  step-1 Join Tables (sub query) ==> step-2 Filtering  (sub query) ==> step-3 Transformation (Sub Query)
==> Step-4 Aggregation(Main Query)
Outer query <== Inner query or Main Query <== (sub query -1<==subquery-2<==subquery-3 <==......)

2. subquery categories:-  

Dependency
i. Non-Correlated subquery: subquery is independent on main query.
ii. correlated subquery: subquery is dependent on main query. 

Result type:-
i. Scalar subquery: return only 1 value
ii. Row subquery: return multiple rows
iii. Table Subquery: returns multiple rows and columns

Location clause:-
i. SELECT
ii. FROM
iii. JOIN
iv. WHERE  1. Comparsion operators i.e., <,>,=,!=,>=,<= 2. Logical operators i.e., IN,ANY,ALL,EXISTS

